'''Nimta Higher Secondary School''', also known as '''Nimta High School''', is a secondary ([[Madhyamik]]) level and [[Higher Secondary School Certificate|Higher Secondary]] (''Uchha Madhyamik'') standard school in [[Nimta]], [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]], India that was established on 1 January 1875. This School is affiliated to [[West Bengal Board of Secondary Education]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Affiliated Schools of West Bengal Board of secondary Education | url= http://wbbse.org/sn24pgs.htm|}}</ref> and [[West Bengal Council of Higher Secondary Education]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Affiliated Schools of West Bengal Council of Higher Secondary Education | url= http://www.webel-india.com/wbchse/html/hs_institute.html}}</ref>

